Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you decide to swipe this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a letter that my mom wrote to me, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're serious about going, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I want your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan once you pass beyond\Nthe Seeker Camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head for the bottom of the Abyss,\Nwhere my mom is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The route from there is-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against it! The bottom of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about it like it's no big deal,\Nbut if you go there you'll never be able to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to be a White Whistle.\NSo I'm already prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Riko, you don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to see any of us up here\Never again, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to hang out at Auntie's,\Nattend Leader's lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or play with any of us here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said... I know that, okay...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you crying about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crying too, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-ouch! I'm not crying a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's call it a night and get some rest.\NNat, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's call it a night and get some rest.\NI'm no dummy. That's you, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is Reg's first cave-raid and all...\NI'm no dummy. That's you, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is Reg's first cave-raid and all...\NJeez, shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!\NJeez, shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-o-ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting"...\NCut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth layer: In the sandstone area of the Sea of Corpses,\NI came across a seven-tailed scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It exceeded two meters in size...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to call it a "stingerhead."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,While sheltering from the rain on the sixth layer,\NI encountered this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a lizard that grows up while still inside its eggshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to its shell,\Nit appears to be unfazed by the iron rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call it an "emperorshell."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearing the seventh layer,\NI came across a human-looking silhouette...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,not sure what is really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For a little while now, it has been intently observing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn idiot, I'm watching you too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the size of a human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't give off the impression of being a Hollow...\Nso perhaps it actually is a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, where did it even come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm getting closer to the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dig up the grass like that,\Nall you're gonna find are bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're set on digging, try that flat spot right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat, what is this thing? It's round and squishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's also a Relic of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno what exactly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got some amazing force holding it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible this could be a special-grade Relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You won't find anything but junk around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe this is junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, if it's junk,\Ndoes that mean it's okay if I keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they'll string up you naked for that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even junk sells for good money over in foreign countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Being an apprentice sure is tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's something else back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to these squishy things in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? You just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What... is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a skeleton of someone in prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Remains like those are from 2,000 years ago, apparently.\NAnd all of 'em are posed that same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you sure freaked out considering you're a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you ever hear this story before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Children who've been eagerly awaiting their birthdays...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have been dying one after the other\Nwhen that day arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The causes for their deaths vary...\Nbut all of them invariably perish on their birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the west district alone,\Nthe count is already up to eight kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor is, if you look into a mirror\Non the morning of your birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your reflection will have a twisted neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you see it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in that kinda stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this robot who's so spooked\Nhe's dripping with sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there is one thing I want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's that "answers lie waiting\Nat the bottom of the netherworld."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The true nature of these Relics...\Nthe cause of the Curse of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps even the meaning behind my creation...\Nor the reason I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't I find answers to all those questions\Nif I reach the bottom of the Abyss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I get, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Riko both...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said yesterday, I'm against going, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're both Red Whistles,\Nand she's still only 12 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after my first cave-raid,\Nmy memory still didn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, the key indeed must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, wait up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...\NNat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Curse of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really are unfazed by it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going at a hell of a pace, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was lost in thought and didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to go fetch somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm okay now. I'm totally fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really am a robot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, that silhouette must also...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiggy mentioned something about an Aubade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm also just a Relic, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I come here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And why doesn't that silhouette come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I come from the bottom of the netherworld...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,have you decided what day you're gonna set off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head out tomorrow just before daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already packed my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure aren't wasting any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how exactly do you plan on\Nslipping into the Abyss, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep watch all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my extending arms to lower you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, I'm going all the way\Nto the bottom of the netherworld along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that you'd be on the side of trying to stop her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Riko enticed you into going, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko didn't say a single thing\Nto try to get me to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to find out just what I am exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet my mom,\Nso hogging you all to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that would be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who found me in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already climbed the Abyss once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my memory doesn't return,\NI have this sturdy body all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you all the way down\Nto the bottom of the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess there's no stopping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll be sad to leave you guys,\Nbut my curiosity got the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we tried to stop her,\NRiko very well may have gone on her own, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Reg, do you have any idea what lies\Nin your path on the way to the netherworld's bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there are a bunch of\Nrandom dangerous creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And Relics and stuff, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you think you can reach the bottom\Nby using your extending arms to descend little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that more or less your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose there'll be some obstacles,\Nbut to be honest that's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How naive! I've gotta say you're far too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Abyss is teeming with dangers\Nbeyond your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the latest Rough Map of the Netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Shiggy! You just went and took it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you're serious about challenging the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking into the director's office\Nis nothing compared to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the current state of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Down to 1,350 meters is the depths' first layer:\Nthe Edge of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The creatures and environment here don't really change,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but beasts from the second layer\Nsometimes come up to feed, so keep your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting here it's the second layer:\Nthe Forest of Temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The strain of ascending\Nis said to suddenly become more severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If a Red Whistle descends down that far,\Nno help will be sent after them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because both heading there\Nand returning home become very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's treated as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest eventually takes the shape of a rat guard,\Nand at that point you enter the Inverted Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The air currents are super unstable\Nand savage predators fill the skies, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The third layer: the Great Fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you'll find a vertical cliff face\Nof over 4,000 meters standing in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth layer: only Black Whistles\Nand above can go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The depth is about 7,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it the Goblet of Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth layer: the Sea of Corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the domain of White Whistles alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can count the number of people\Nwho've returned from here on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixth layer: the Capital of the Unreturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When a White Whistle descends to the sixth layer,\Npeople call it their "last dive."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they'll never be able to return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any cases of someone who's not a\NWhite Whistle going down lower than the sixth layer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone other than a White Whistle\Nsends information up from the Abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be considered "mere rumor."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's possible the Curse of the Abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,caused the person to become confused\Nor even go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if the voice of a White Whistle\Nreaches the surface, it will be considered "truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The voices of White Whistles are the voices of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a White Whistle loses his life,\Nhe lives on as a voice of the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and guides everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, that letter is for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Riko, sorry to bring this up\Nwhen you're so fired up to go-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I'm still going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom is waiting for me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you even been paying attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Think anyone could live\Nsomewhere like that for 10 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did her whistle make its way to the surface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom died a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lowered the luggage and spare clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With this on, you think they'll be able to tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Nat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Right now Nat is probably-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what that guy's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat was so worried about you\Nthat he ended up crossing the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko... you might never get the chance\Nto see him again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to just\Nleave things unresolved like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sure don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he's against us going...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said some nasty stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reg, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, if Nat apologizes, will you forgive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can be quite stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Nat was regretting what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get going soon, you'll run out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So as not to draw attention,\Nwe'll all leave one by one in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiggy, you want a hand, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get down there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiggy, I'm sorry, but there's still something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but be really careful not to get caught by Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he with Riko and Shiggy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyui... Kiyui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you've been\Nlooking like you're always sleepy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I hope you get better before your big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up nice and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyui, on the morning of your birthday,\Ndon't look into a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That took longer than I thought. I've gotta hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,T-to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any toilets in that room, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was still half asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader, what are you doing up\Nin the middle of the night yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, I'm on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I do this every night after you all fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea where Riko is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be in her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko... went to take a dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She scavenging for food again? Jeez, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your way to the toilet too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with her and make sure she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiggy, we're headed off to the wharf quarter now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the usual Gate to the Netherworld\Nis always closely guarded, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the wharf quarter in the slums\Nhas a good spot to enter from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You "hear"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never actually been to the wharf quarter before...\Nso I called someone to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wrong... what I did yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so, even though I said such terrible things you still...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Today... is the day we say farewell, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you don't know the way to the wharf quarter, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Nat, you're helping us out\Nbecause you're okay with us going now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, you oppose it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, Nat. Glad you came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Riko and I will both be able to send off\Nour letters without any reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The first or second layers are one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but from where you're going\Na mail balloon will never make it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well even for a White Whistle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the odds of a mail balloon making it to the surface\Nfrom the deeper depths are VERY low.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright! I'll send a ton of 'em, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet my mother did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this "At the netherworld's bottom, I'll be waiting"\Nlooks like it was scrawled out hastily...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps she sent several\Ndifferent sealed documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then put one of these inside each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Riko, I was thinking one of your fanciful ideas\Nsurprisingly makes sense for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this still part of Orth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The wharf district, you see, was founded by people\Nwho were cave-raiding illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Buildings kept being added on as the quarter grew,\Nand now half it is encroaching into the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! You're being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't look around at everything so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat, have you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was rag-picking ever since I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sis died so I was left without any relatives,\Nand then I was taken in by the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the story I told Leader\Nwhen I first entered the orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids around here all see that Gate to the Netherworld\Nand start aspiring to be cave raiders...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lucky and was taken in off the streets...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, like everyone else here, I would've\Ngotten sick from the toxins in the garbage or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can become a Moon Whistle like Leader,\NI'd like to open an orphanage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat, you of all people can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just about as good at cave-raiding as I am,\Nand you're full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you come up with\Nsome better compliments than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this thing really does fit me to a T.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where did I put that whistle...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a real possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have an Aubade with you, so I'll definitely be\Na believer if one of your mail balloons makes it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll make sure to include a souvenir\Nwith each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep on waiting as long as I need to, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...\NI'll keep on waiting as long as I need to, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really amazing, Nat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought we'd make it out here\Nwith so little trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I thought about it so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we never get to see each other again,\Nwe'll be connected by the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's on the surface...\Nor in the far reaches of the cursed netherworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us... are connected to the Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget about the time I spent up here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm at it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! Some of the residents are awake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those brats?!\NOh, crap! Some of the residents are awake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You better send some letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to find them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's fine if you decide to\Nhead right on back here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to take care of Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. You guys care take of yourselves, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye out for the good news I'll be sending!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we're off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading into the chasm\Nfor which even darkness is no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who offer up their bodies and challenge it,\Nthe Abyss is said to provide all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Life and death, curses and blessings - all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of their journeys,\Nwhat will they come to finally choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that be determined by the will of the netherworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will it be determined solely by those who challenge it?
